    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "This E46 M3 is a purist\u2019s driver, powered by the high-revving S54 3.2L inline-six with individual throttle bodies. The powertrain is in excellent mechanical health, featuring a recently serviced VANOS system and a reinforced rear subframe to ensure chassis longevity. The Getrag 6-speed manual transmission offers precise throws, paired with a factory limited-slip differential that maintains exceptional traction out of corners. While the exterior shows minor road wear, the mechanical components\u2014including refreshed suspension bushings and upgraded cooling\u2014are dialed in for spirited performance. A technically sound example of BMW\u2019s finest naturally aspirated era.",
