    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "Up for sale is a meticulously maintained vehicle that strikes the perfect balance between luxury and everyday utility. The exterior retains a deep, lustrous shine, though a close inspection will reveal a few minor stone chips on the front bumper and a small scuff on the rear passenger door\u2014typical for a car that has been enjoyed on the road. Inside, the cabin is smoke-free and remarkably clean; the leather seats show light bolster wear but remain supple and supportive. All onboard electronics, including the infotainment system and dual-zone climate control, function exactly as they should. Under the hood, the engine runs smoothly with a consistent service history, most recently receiving a full synthetic oil change and a fresh set of brake pads. The tires have plenty of tread remaining, ensuring a confident grip in all weather conditions. This car has been a reliable companion and is ready for its next owner to drive it home with peace of mind.",
      "price": 34500.0,
